# Kinshasa Backend (fresh)

## Setup local
1. Copier `.env` avec:
   - MONGO_URI=<your mongo uri>
   - FIREBASE_KEY=<json stringified firebase service account (optional)>

2. Installer:
3. Lancer en dev:
## Routes utiles
- GET  /api/users
- POST /api/users          { name, email }
- GET  /api/reports
- POST /api/reports       { title, description, location? }
- PATCH /api/reports/:id  { status: "nouveau"|"en cours"|"trait√©" }
